Discord Poll Bot\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Create, share, and track polls across your Discord servers.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:alt\" content=\"Polly — Discord Poll Bot\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:type\" content=\"image/png\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://polly.pudding.vip/opengraph-image?b7dee98f2c875cdb\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon-16x16.png\" sizes=\"16x16\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon-32x32.png\" sizes=\"32x32\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\" sizes=\"180x180\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/site.webmanifest\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"flex flex-col min-h-screen\"><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-p-bg/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-p-border/60\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 h-16 flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 shrink-0\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Polly\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-xl\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Favatar.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Favatar.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Favatar.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"font-display font-bold text-lg text-p-text\">Polly</span></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm transition-all text-p-text bg-p-surface-2 font-medium\" href=\"/\">Home</a></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=undefined&amp;permissions=274878024704&amp;scope=bot%20applications.commands\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"btn-secondary text-sm py-2\">Add to Discord</a><button class=\"btn-discord\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-log-in\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m10 17 5-5-5-5\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-4\"></path></svg>Sign in</button></div></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 text-p-muted hover:text-p-text\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"min-h-screen\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--><section class=\"relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pt-20 pb-24 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 badge badge-primary mb-6 text-sm px-3 py-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg>Discord Poll Bot</div><h1 class=\"font-display font-bold text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl leading-tight mb-6\"><span class=\"heading-display\">Polls that live</span><br/><span class=\"text-p-text\">inside Discord</span></h1><p class=\"text-p-muted text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed\">Create polls, schedule events with time slot voting, and let your community decide — all without leaving Discord. Manage everything from a clean web dashboard.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"btn-primary text-base px-6 py-3 gap-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-external-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"M10 14 21 3\"></path><path d=\"M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6\"></path></svg>Add Polly to Discord</a><a class=\"btn-secondary text-base px-6 py-3\" href=\"/dashboard\">Open Dashboard<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-p-text mb-3\">Everything you need</h2><p class=\"text-p-muted text-lg\">Packed with features, designed to stay out of your way.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"card-hover p-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-p-primary-b flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-vote text-p-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M5 7c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12H5V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M22 19H2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-2\">In-Discord Voting</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Polls live right in your server. Members vote with a single button click — no links, no friction.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-p-accent-b flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column text-p-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-2\">Live Results</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Results update in real-time on both Discord and the web dashboard as votes come in.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-p-primary-b flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-p-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-2\">Time Slot Voting</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Add time preferences to any poll — voters pick their option then their preferred time, perfect for scheduling events.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-p-accent-b flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users text-p-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-2\">Multi-Server</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">One bot, many servers. Each Discord gets its own dashboard, polls, and settings.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-p-primary-b flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield text-p-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-2\">Role-Based Access</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Control who can create polls and who can vote — per server, using Discord roles.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-p-accent-b flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap text-p-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-2\">Dashboard Embed</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Pin a live dashboard in any channel. Create polls and view results without leaving Discord.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 badge badge-primary mb-5 text-sm px-3 py-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>Time Slot Voting</div><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-p-text mb-4\">Stop the back-and-forth.<br/>Find a time that works.</h2><p class=\"text-p-muted text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Attach time preferences to any poll. Voters choose their favourite option <em>and</em> their preferred time — Polly collects both in one step.</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-p-muted text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-p-success shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Voters see times converted to their own timezone</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-p-muted text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-p-success shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Works with any poll — events, raids, meetings, anything</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-p-muted text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-p-success shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Time results shown separately so you can find the overlap</li></ul></div><div class=\"card p-5 space-y-4 shadow-xl shadow-black/30\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-p-primary-b flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-vote text-p-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M5 7c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12H5V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M22 19H2\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-p-text font-semibold text-sm\">Which day for the FC raid?</p><p class=\"text-p-muted text-xs\">6 votes · closes in 2 days</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-1\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-p-primary\">Friday</span><span class=\"text-p-muted text-xs\">3<!-- --> · <!-- -->50<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full bg-p-surface-2 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full bg-p-primary\" style=\"width:50%\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-1\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-p-text\">Saturday</span><span class=\"text-p-muted text-xs\">2<!-- --> · <!-- -->33<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full bg-p-surface-2 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full bg-p-muted/40\" style=\"width:33%\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-1\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-p-text\">Sunday</span><span class=\"text-p-muted text-xs\">1<!-- --> · <!-- -->17<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full bg-p-surface-2 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full bg-p-muted/40\" style=\"width:17%\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-p-border pt-3\"><p class=\"text-p-muted text-xs mb-2.5\">You voted <strong class=\"text-p-text\">Friday</strong> — pick a preferred time:</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"badge px-3 py-1.5 text-xs badge-muted\">7pm</span><span class=\"badge px-3 py-1.5 text-xs badge-primary\">8pm</span><span class=\"badge px-3 py-1.5 text-xs badge-muted\">9pm</span><span class=\"badge px-3 py-1.5 text-xs badge-muted\">10pm</span><span class=\"badge px-3 py-1.5 text-xs badge-muted\">No preference</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-p-text mb-3\">How it works</h2><p class=\"text-p-muted text-lg\">Up and running in under two minutes.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><div class=\"card p-6\"><div class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl text-p-primary/30 mb-3\">01</div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-1.5\">Invite Polly</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm\">Add the bot to your Discord server in one click.</p></div><div class=\"card p-6\"><div class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl text-p-primary/30 mb-3\">02</div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-1.5\">Sign in</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm\">Log in with Discord to see your server&#x27;s dashboard.</p></div><div class=\"card p-6\"><div class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl text-p-primary/30 mb-3\">03</div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-1.5\">Create a poll</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm\">Fill in the title, options, and optional close time.</p></div><div class=\"card p-6\"><div class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl text-p-primary/30 mb-3\">04</div><h3 class=\"font-display font-semibold text-p-text mb-1.5\">Members vote</h3><p class=\"text-p-muted text-sm\">Your server votes via Discord buttons or the web page.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24\"><div class=\"card-primary p-10 text-center rounded-2xl\"><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold text-3xl text-p-text mb-3\">Ready to start polling?</h2><p class=\"text-p-muted mb-8\">Add Polly to your server and run your first poll in minutes.</p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"btn-primary text-base px-8 py-3 inline-flex mx-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-external-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"M10 14 21 3\"></path><path d=\"M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6\"></path></svg>Add to Discord — it&#x27;s free</a></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-p-border mt-20 py-10 text-p-muted text-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-p-primary-b border border-p-primary/40 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-vote text-p-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M5 7c0-1.1.9-2 2-2